{"tid":2517346,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳偉豪疑似不雅片流出就要「雪」？ 何遠東隨時候命準備加入愛回家","createTime":"2021-05-05T09:12:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T10:16:09.000Z","uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f7f519ec6a9b09342f8c1ac6376ac3b987019850","tid":2517346,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:12:33.000Z","msg":"無綫藝員吳偉豪（Ricco）有疑似不雅片段在網上討論區流出，流出一小時內就已在網上瘋傳，不過翌日TVB高層樂易玲小姐回覆傳媒時，就表示吳偉豪已經與家人漏夜到警署報案。事發後多日，疑似不雅片段事主吳偉豪依舊沒有公開澄清或者承認，而網民最關心的除了片段中的細節外，就最關心無綫會不會因此而「雪藏」吳偉豪。<br />\n<br />\n就以馬賽為例，她在2008年參選香港小姐時，就獲傳媒封為「的骰桂綸鎂」的名，其後更同時奪得季軍及最上鏡小姐，與同屆的冠軍張舒雅、亞軍陳倩揚以及高海寧一同加入TVB發展。2010年開始更獲機會參演《女王辦公室》、《名媛望族》等劇集，而2013年11月，就爆出馬賽同性戀事件，否認傳聞後隨後再遭傳媒登出證據，「潛水」後亦令她形象大跌。時任無綫製作資源部總監樂易玲才下「雪藏」令，休假兩個月。<br />\n<br />\n翌年7月份遭傳媒登出跳艷舞照片，停工超過三個月後也正式復工，獲機會參演劇集《東坡家事》以及擔任娛樂新聞國語台主持。可見無綫電視在多年前，對旗下藝人不雅照流出，會採取「先停工，冷靜一段時間，後再慢慢安排工作」的政策，務求將傷害減至最低。馬賽於2015年離開TVB，其實也只是因為發展不佳而不續約。<br />\n<br />\n不過TVB為了以防萬一，地下消息指出何遠東準備加入愛回家大學線，以學長身份出現在未來主線。何遠東近年搞笑形象相當入屋，其演藝實力也備受觀眾肯定，更有觀眾稱他為未來視帝候選，加上近來傳出他將出任新千禧五虎，相信是無線力捧小生。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeGCCX2VcEpHBCyVXUSU9cajRZ9PBB5SQk8VQnXgFiGLg?filename=A6RCLkk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA6RCLkk.jpg&h=664f6f6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmeBocpPJnGKk5WP5f2wPTHbQBH5iiEkGs2YhA6LJFJMvd?filename=KTtQ5ks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTtQ5ks.jpg&h=7e435d3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19327c72a4ec482c49b3c2af0f37b3c13341de03","tid":2517346,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:14:48.000Z","msg":"不過呢 大個仔喇 唔好再犯"},{"pid":"44087bb2f03eb146cdd115549790f93d75004e5a","tid":2517346,"uid":123696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:15:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾稿<br />\n<br />\n淨係講之前TVB會點點點<br />\n又無消息話佢係咪真係畀人雪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實佢應該學email咁 化危為機 索性做脫星<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a27902fea154a88ab09fa378cf8cc47ac980f9","tid":2517346,"uid":31841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:17:32.000Z","msg":"佢搵多幾隻騎呢怪組tvb error好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1511044bf4e1c374b727850f8e3e1371e8a20f6b","tid":2517346,"uid":378363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:18:26.000Z","msg":"未來視帝候選<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人才凋零到咁嘅地步"},{"pid":"39f1c971b6e9423c3a50b3d69b3ecde1cb586627","tid":2517346,"uid":1262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:20:29.000Z","msg":"懷疑樓主係白卡仔打手"},{"pid":"fc29acf879d0f1d44ec525760f7e358b6038e334","tid":2517346,"uid":195581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:28:39.000Z","msg":"佢唔係減咗肥咩?做咩仲係咁肥?"},{"pid":"991f2b6cb06c1e369fc69ca9e71263e67235b9b5","tid":2517346,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:00:17.000Z","msg":"肥仔收皮"},{"pid":"08a87c7d9e4f4578a1e69e8466d89c6d50ffe2db","tid":2517346,"uid":165665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T10:06:27.000Z","msg":"厹樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"421e53cd682f055a682b8973e11c9617885fc1c3","tid":2517346,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-